        "hint": "Copy-as-you-want share-extension export. Carries `preset` (true = shipped preset, false = user-authored custom template) and `changed`. Preset/custom mix is the customization-adoption read (insight 18); a custom-leaning mix is the strongest Pro signal."
      },
      {
        "type": "event",
        "name": "Intent.Clean.succeeded",
